      <t>&lt;p&gt;The intention of this document, in conjunction with RFC 2958, is to enable MIME-enabled mail software, and other systems using Internet media types, to carry out Whois++ transactions.  This memo provides information for the Internet community.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
